'''''Greatest Hits''''' is a compilation album by [[Canadian]] [[Rock music|rock]] [[Musical ensemble|band]] [[April Wine]] released in 1979.<ref name="allmusic1" /> The picture on this album cover is also used on three other albums ''[[First Glance]]'' (1978) <small>(American version only)</small>, ''[[The Hits (April Wine album)|The Hits]]'' (1987), and ''[[Classic Masters (April Wine album)|Classic Masters]]'' (2002).

